THE SECURITY GUARDS

460
00:31:26,968 --> 00:31:28,554
TO ENFORCE IT?

461
00:32:00,836 --> 00:32:02,588
[LAUGHING]

462
00:32:09,344 --> 00:32:10,721
MIRAMANEE.

463
00:32:17,728 --> 00:32:18,645
COME HERE.

464
00:32:27,696 --> 00:32:28,655
MIRAMANEE.

465
00:32:41,418 --> 00:32:43,253
EACH TIME
YOUR ARMS HOLD ME

466
00:32:43,378 --> 00:32:45,505
IS AS JOYOUS
AS THE FIRST.

467
00:32:45,631 --> 00:32:47,132
I'M HAPPY.

468
00:32:47,257 --> 00:32:49,426
I'M SO HAPPY.

469
00:32:52,262 --> 00:32:54,514
IF IT WEREN'T
FOR THE DREAMS, I...

470
00:32:54,640 --> 00:32:58,101
