THROUGH THE SKY.

474
00:33:07,026 --> 00:33:09,738
THEY'VE COME BACK.

475
00:33:10,405 --> 00:33:12,783
THEY WERE GONE
FOR A WHILE,

476
00:33:12,908 --> 00:33:14,910
BUT THEY'VE COME BACK,

477
00:33:15,034 --> 00:33:17,203
AND I...

478
00:33:18,121 --> 00:33:21,249
