479
00:33:21,374 --> 00:33:23,251
VERY DIM.

480
00:33:23,376 --> 00:33:25,921
I FEEL...

481
00:33:26,045 --> 00:33:28,966
I SHOULD KNOW--KNOW THEM.

482
00:33:30,383 --> 00:33:32,636
I FEEL...

483
00:33:32,761 --> 00:33:34,930
MY PLACE IS WITH THEM,

484
00:33:35,054 --> 00:33:38,350
NOT HERE.

485
00:33:39,142 --> 00:33:42,354
I DON'T DESERVE
THIS HAPPINESS.

486
00:33:43,981 --> 00:33:46,733
I HAVE A GIFT
FOR YOU.

487
00:33:48,026 --> 00:33:49,110
GIFT?

488
00:33:53,406 --> 00:33:54,741
WHAT?

489
00:33:55,617 --> 00:33:57,744
IT MAY
MAKE YOU HAPPY.

490
00:33:58,411 --> 00:34:00,413
WAIT.

491
00:34:00,539 --> 00:34:02,499
<i>[THINKING]</i>
<i>THESE LAST FEW WEEKS,</i>

492
00:34:02,624 --> 00:34:04,960
<i>MY LOVE FOR MIRAMANEE</i>
<i>GROWS STRONGER</i>

493
00:34:05,084 --> 00:34:06,753
<i>WITH EACH PASSING DAY.</i>

494
00:34:06,879 --> 00:34:10,799
<i>HOWEVER, THE DREAMS RETURN</i>
<i>EVERY NIGHT...</i>

495
00:34:10,924 --> 00:34:12,467
<i>FRAGMENTS OF MEMORIES.</i>

496
00:34:12,592 --> 00:34:16,889
<i>I CAN ALMOST</i>
<i>GET HOLD OF THEM,</i>

497
00:34:17,014 --> 00:34:19,140
<i>AND THEN...</i>

498
00:34:26,732 --> 00:34:28,734
I BEAR YOUR CHILD.

499
00:34:36,366 --> 00:34:37,283
[LAUGHS]

500
00:34:37,409 --> 00:34:38,827
YOU...

501
00:34:44,374 --> 00:34:47,335
[LAUGHING]

502
00:34:55,052 --> 00:34:56,428
A CANAL...

503
00:34:56,553 --> 00:34:59,932
AND WITH IT, WE'LL
BRING THE WATER

504
00:35:00,057 --> 00:35:02,017
FROM THE LAKE

505
00:35:02,141 --> 00:35:04,227
RIGHT TO THE LODGE.

506
00:35:04,352 --> 00:35:06,271
AND WE CAN EXPAND
THE SYSTEM...

507
00:35:06,396 --> 00:35:08,481
SEE...

508
00:35:08,607 --> 00:35:10,400
AND IRRIGATE
THE FIELDS

509
00:35:10,525 --> 00:35:13,486
AND DOUBLE
THE FOOD SUPPLY.

510
00:35:13,612 --> 00:35:16,281
AND WITH THE POWER
OF THE LAMP...

511
00:35:16,406 --> 00:35:17,282
LAMP?

512
00:35:17,407 --> 00:35:18,491
LAMP.

513
00:35:18,617 --> 00:35:20,493
WHICH TURNS NIGHT
INTO DAY,

514
00:35:20,619 --> 00:35:23,038
WE CAN COOK
TWICE AS MUCH FOOD,

515
00:35:23,162 --> 00:35:24,414
AND AS YOU TAUGHT US...

516
00:35:24,539 --> 00:35:25,916
PRE...

517
00:35:26,041 --> 00:35:26,959
PRESERVE.

518
00:35:27,084 --> 00:35:27,960
PRESERVE.

519
00:35:28,085 --> 00:35:29,836
PRESERVE.

520
00:35:29,962 --> 00:35:31,880
FAMINE.
FOR TIMES OF FAMINE.

521
00:35:32,005 --> 00:35:33,465
[BOTH CHUCKLE]

522
00:35:33,590 --> 00:35:35,801
THAT IS WHY YOU MADE
THE LAMP, KIROK,

523
00:35:35,926 --> 00:35:37,636
