NEVER KNOW WHEN
IT WAS NIGHT

524
00:35:37,761 --> 00:35:39,178
AND I WOULD BE
FOREVER COOKING.

525
00:35:39,304 --> 00:35:41,389
OH, NO. NO, NO, NO, NO.

526
00:35:41,514 --> 00:35:43,516
THAT'S NOT WHY
I MADE THE LAMP AT ALL,

527
00:35:43,642 --> 00:35:45,769
TO KEEP YOU
FOREVER COOKING.

528
00:35:47,062 --> 00:35:49,606
[THUNDER AND WIND HOWLING]

529
00:35:51,942 --> 00:35:54,903
IT'S ONLY THE WIND...

530
00:35:55,028 --> 00:35:56,738
AND THE THUNDER.

531
00:35:57,614 --> 00:35:59,407
I ACT LIKE
A STUPID CHILD.

532
00:35:59,532 --> 00:36:00,993
I HAVE NOTHING
TO FEAR.

533
00:36:01,118 --> 00:36:02,828
YOU ARE HERE.

534
00:36:10,752 --> 00:36:12,211
IT IS TIME.

535
00:36:12,337 --> 00:36:14,965
TIME?

536
00:36:15,090 --> 00:36:16,508
TO GO TO THE TEMPLE.
THE PEOPLE WILL BE WAITING.

537
00:36:16,633 --> 00:36:17,717
WHY?

538
00:36:17,843 --> 00:36:18,259
TO SAVE THEM.

539
00:36:18,384 --> 00:36:20,095
BUT IT'S ONLY
THE WIND.

540
00:36:20,219 --> 00:36:21,596
THE WIND
CAN'T HARM THEM.

541
00:36:21,721 --> 00:36:23,515
THE WIND IS ONLY
THE BEGINNING.

542
00:36:23,640 --> 00:36:24,933
SOON THE SKY
WILL DARKEN,

543
00:36:25,058 --> 00:36:26,518
THE LAKE WILL GO WILD,

544
00:36:26,643 --> 00:36:27,936
AND THE EARTH
WILL TREMBLE.

545
00:36:28,061 --> 00:36:30,147
ONLY YOU CAN SAVE US.

546
00:36:30,271 --> 00:36:31,898
BUT I CAN'T
DO ANYTHING

547
00:36:32,024 --> 00:36:34,734
ABOUT THE WIND
OR THE SKY.

548
00:36:34,860 --> 00:36:37,737
IF WE DO NOT GO NOW,
IT WILL BE TOO LATE.

549
00:36:37,863 --> 00:36:38,989
YOU MUST GO
INSIDE THE TEMPLE

550
00:36:39,114 --> 00:36:41,366
AND MAKE THE BLUE FLAME
COME OUT.

551
00:36:41,491 --> 00:36:45,037
I DON'T KNOW HOW
TO GET INSIDE
THE TEMPLE.

552
00:36:45,162 --> 00:36:47,122
BUT YOU ARE A GOD.

553
00:36:49,207 --> 00:36:50,291
KIROK!

554
00:36:50,416 --> 00:36:52,377
KIROK!

555
00:36:52,502 --> 00:36:55,463
WHY ARE YOU NOT
AT THE TEMPLE, KIROK?

556
00:36:55,588 --> 00:36:57,215
SOON THE GROUND
WILL BEGIN TO TREMBLE.

557
00:36:57,340 --> 00:37:00,010
THE PEOPLE NEED
YOUR HELP.

558
00:37:00,135 --> 00:37:01,720
WE'LL GO TO THE CAVES.

559
00:37:01,845 --> 00:37:03,805
IT'LL BE SAFE THERE.

560
00:37:03,930 --> 00:37:05,431
THE CAVES?

561
00:37:05,557 --> 00:37:07,017
SURELY A LEGEND
CAN DO MORE THAN THAT

562
00:37:07,142 --> 00:37:09,144
FOR HIS PEOPLE.

563
00:37:09,268 --> 00:37:12,022
WHEN THE GROUND TREMBLES,
THE CAVES ARE NOT SAFE, KIROK.

564
00:37:12,147 --> 00:37:13,940
IF YOU DO NOT ROUSE
THE TEMPLE SPIRIT,

565
00:37:14,066 --> 00:37:15,650
WE WILL ALL DIE.

566
00:37:15,775 --> 00:37:18,987
THERE IS NOTHING
YOU CANNOT DO,
MY HUSBAND.

567
00:37:19,112 --> 00:37:22,032
WELL, WHAT DO YOU
WAIT FOR, GOD?

568
00:37:22,157 --> 00:37:23,449
YOUR ROBES?

569
00:37:29,330 --> 00:37:31,958
TAKE CARE OF MIRAMANEE,

570
00:38:03,489 --> 00:38:05,951
I AM KIROK!

571
00:38:07,077 --> 00:38:09,621
I HAVE COME!

572
00:38:09,746 --> 00:38:13,083
I AM KIROK!

573
00:38:30,225 --> 00:38:31,309
I PRESCRIBED SLEEP.

574
00:38:31,434 --> 00:38:33,603
YOU PRESCRIBED REST,
DOCTOR.

575
00:38:33,728 --> 00:38:36,439
THE SYMBOLS
ON THE OBELISK
ARE NOT WORDS.

576
00:38:36,564 --> 00:38:38,108
THEY ARE
MUSICAL NOTES.

577
00:38:38,233 --> 00:38:39,151
MUSICAL NOTES?

578
00:38:39,276 --> 00:38:40,986
YOU MEAN IT'S NOTHING
BUT A SONG?

579
00:38:41,111 --> 00:38:42,528
IN A WAY, YES.

580
00:38:42,654 --> 00:38:44,948
OTHER CULTURES,
AMONG THEM CERTAIN
VULCAN OFFSHOOTS,

581
00:38:45,073 --> 00:38:46,825
USE MUSICAL NOTES
AS WORDS.

582
00:38:46,950 --> 00:38:49,744
THE TONES
CORRESPOND ROUGHLY
TO AN ALPHABET.

583
00:38:49,869 --> 00:38:51,913
WERE YOU ABLE
TO MAKE ANY SENSE
OF THE SYMBOLS?

584
00:38:52,038 --> 00:38:54,415
YES. THE OBELISK
IS A MARKER,
JUST AS I THOUGHT.

585
00:38:54,540 --> 00:38:56,584
IT WAS LEFT
BY A SUPER RACE

586
00:38:56,709 --> 00:38:58,336
KNOWN AS
THE PRESERVERS.

587
00:38:58,461 --> 00:38:59,963
THEY PASSED
THROUGH THE GALAXY

588
00:39:00,088 --> 00:39:01,380
RESCUING
PRIMITIVE CULTURES

589
00:39:01,506 --> 00:39:03,675
WHICH WERE IN DANGER
OF EXTINCTION

590
00:39:03,800 --> 00:39:05,302
AND SEEDING THEM,
SO TO SPEAK,

591
00:39:05,426 --> 00:39:07,846
WHERE THEY COULD
LIVE AND GROW.

592
00:39:07,971 --> 00:39:10,056
I'VE ALWAYS WONDERED
WHY THERE WERE
SO MANY HUMANOIDS

593
00:39:10,182 --> 00:39:11,599
SCATTERED THROUGH
THE GALAXY.

594
00:39:11,724 --> 00:39:13,351
SO HAVE I. APPARENTLY,
THE PRESERVERS

595
00:39:13,476 --> 00:39:15,187
ACCOUNT FOR
A NUMBER OF THEM.

596
00:39:15,312 --> 00:39:17,105
THAT'S PROBABLY HOW
THE PLANET HAS SURVIVED

597
00:39:17,230 --> 00:39:18,606
ALL THESE CENTURIES.

598
00:39:18,731 --> 00:39:20,942
THE PRESERVERS PUT
AN ASTEROID DEFLECTOR
ON THE PLANET.

599
00:39:21,067 --> 00:39:22,652
WHICH HAS NOW
BECOME DEFECTIVE

600
00:39:22,777 --> 00:39:24,196
AND IS FAILING
TO OPERATE.

601
00:39:24,321 --> 00:39:26,281
AND WE HAVE TO
FIND THAT DEFLECTOR

602
00:39:26,405 --> 00:39:29,075
AND PUT IT BACK
INTO WORKING ORDER.
OTHERWISE...

603
00:39:29,201 --> 00:39:31,369
PRECISELY, DOCTOR.

604
00:39:33,496 --> 00:39:35,665
THERE'S THE FALSE ONE!

605
00:39:35,790 --> 00:39:38,918
DIE! DIE! DIE!

606
00:39:40,378 --> 00:39:43,506
NO! NO! DON'T HURT HIM!

607
00:39:44,007 --> 00:39:45,258
MIRAMANEE!

608
00:39:45,383 --> 00:39:47,593
DON'T HURT HIM!
HE CAN SAVE US!

609
00:39:47,719 --> 00:39:49,971
HE'S FALSE!

610
00:39:50,096 --> 00:39:51,764
I BELONG TO HIM.

611
00:39:51,890 --> 00:39:53,308
THEN GO.

612
00:39:53,432 --> 00:39:57,020
GO DIE WITH
YOUR FALSE GOD.

613
00:39:57,145 --> 00:39:58,646
YOU'LL BE KILLED!

614
00:39:58,771 --> 00:39:59,898
[SHOUTING]

615
00:40:00,023 --> 00:40:02,150
KILL THEM!

616
00:40:02,275 --> 00:40:05,070
WE'RE ALL DOOMED!

617
00:40:05,195 --> 00:40:08,323
MURDER THE IMPOSTOR!

618
00:40:08,447 --> 00:40:09,532
YOU LIED TO US!

619
00:40:09,657 --> 00:40:13,619
YOU'RE NOT A GOD!
WE'LL KILL YOU NOW!

620
00:40:37,518 --> 00:40:39,645
I NEED NURSE CHAPEL.

621
00:40:40,855 --> 00:40:41,940
SPOCK TO<i> ENTERPRISE.</i>

622
00:40:42,065 --> 00:40:42,982
Scott:
COME IN, MR. SPOCK.

623
00:40:43,108 --> 00:40:44,359
WE'VE LOCATED THE CAPTAIN.

624
00:40:44,483 --> 00:40:45,402
BEAM DOWN NURSE CHAPEL

625
00:40:45,526 --> 00:40:47,612
WITH AN EMERGENCY
SURGICAL KIT.

626
00:40:51,490 --> 00:40:53,368
MY WIFE...

627
00:40:53,492 --> 00:40:55,620
IS SHE ALL RIGHT?

628
00:40:55,745 --> 00:40:57,372
WIFE?

629
00:40:57,496 --> 00:40:58,748
HALLUCINATIONS?

630
00:40:58,873 --> 00:41:00,833
JIM.

631
00:41:00,959 --> 00:41:02,210
MIRAMANEE.

632
00:41:07,424 --> 00:41:09,217
MIRAMANEE.

633
00:41:30,029 --> 00:41:33,283
THE NURSE HAS
GIVEN YOU SOMETHING
TO EASE THE PAIN.

634
00:41:33,408 --> 00:41:36,577
WHY WERE YOU
BEING STONED?

635
00:41:38,997 --> 00:41:42,750
KIROK COULD NOT GET BACK

636
00:41:42,875 --> 00:41:44,919
INTO THE TEMPLE.

637
00:41:45,044 --> 00:41:48,589
NATURALLY,
SINCE HE DID NOT
COME FROM THERE.

638
00:41:50,883 --> 00:41:54,095
I SAW HIM COME--COME.

639
00:42:05,482 --> 00:42:07,066
DOES HE RECOGNIZE US?

640
00:42:07,192 --> 00:42:08,943
HIS BRAIN
IS UNIMPAIRED.

641
00:42:09,068 --> 00:42:10,111
EVERYTHING ELSE
IS FUNCTIONALLY
NORMALLY

642
00:42:10,236 --> 00:42:11,737
EXCEPT HIS MEMORY.

643
00:42:11,863 --> 00:42:13,281
CAN YOU HELP HIM?

644
00:42:13,406 --> 00:42:14,657
IT'D TAKE TIME.

645
00:42:14,782 --> 00:42:15,825
TIME, DR. McCOY,
IS THE ONE THING

646
00:42:15,950 --> 00:42:18,077
WE DO NOT HAVE
IN ABUNDANCE.

647
00:42:18,203 --> 00:42:20,079
[COMMUNICATOR BEEPS]

648
00:42:20,205 --> 00:42:21,331
SPOCK HERE.

649
00:42:21,456 --> 00:42:22,499
Sulu:
TRACKING REPORT, SIR.

650
00:42:22,623 --> 00:42:25,418
65 MINUTES TO END
OF SAFETY MARGIN.

651
00:42:25,543 --> 00:42:28,546
REPORT NOTED.

652
00:42:30,507 --> 00:42:32,384
DOCTOR, IS HE STRONG ENOUGH

653
00:42:32,509 --> 00:42:34,386
FOR THE VULCAN MIND FUSION?

654
00:42:34,511 --> 00:42:35,636
WE HAVE NO CHOICE.

655
00:42:46,856 --> 00:42:51,361
I AM SPOCK.

656
00:42:51,486 --> 00:42:54,906
YOU ARE JAMES KIRK.

657
00:42:55,031 --> 00:42:58,951
OUR MINDS
ARE MOVING CLOSER...

658
00:42:59,077 --> 00:43:00,412
CLOSER...

659
00:43:00,537 --> 00:43:02,288
CLOSER...

660
00:43:02,414 --> 00:43:04,332
CLOSER, JAMES KIRK.

661
00:43:04,457 --> 00:43:06,376
CLOSER.

662
00:43:07,668 --> 00:43:09,003
NO!

663
00:43:09,128 --> 00:43:10,838
JAMES KIRK.

664
00:43:10,963 --> 00:43:11,964
MIRAMANEE!

665
00:43:12,090 --> 00:43:13,049
NO!

666
00:43:13,174 --> 00:43:14,592
MIRAMANEE!

667
00:43:14,717 --> 00:43:17,262
OUR MINDS...

668
00:43:17,387 --> 00:43:19,013
