669
00:43:21,099 --> 00:43:23,351
I...

670
00:43:23,476 --> 00:43:25,978
AM...

671
00:43:26,104 --> 00:43:28,565
KIROK.

672
00:43:28,689 --> 00:43:29,857
I...

673
00:43:29,982 --> 00:43:31,943
AM...

674
00:43:32,068 --> 00:43:32,902
KIROK.

675
00:43:33,027 --> 00:43:36,781
I AM KIR--

676
00:43:38,657 --> 00:43:40,452
I...

677
00:43:40,577 --> 00:43:42,620
AM KIROK!

678
00:43:44,080 --> 00:43:45,790
I AM...

679
00:43:45,915 --> 00:43:47,459
SPOCK!

680
00:43:50,169 --> 00:43:51,963
WHAT IS IT?

681
00:43:52,088 --> 00:43:54,299
HIS MIND...

682
00:43:54,424 --> 00:43:56,593
HE IS...

683
00:43:56,717 --> 00:44:00,346
AN EXTREMELY
DYNAMIC INDIVIDUAL.

684
00:44:08,938 --> 00:44:10,523
IT WORKED.

685
00:44:18,448 --> 00:44:20,741
CAPTAIN, WERE YOU
INSIDE THIS STRUCTURE?

686
00:44:20,866 --> 00:44:24,662
YES. WHAT'S INSIDE
IS LOADED

687
00:44:24,787 --> 00:44:25,704
WITH SCIENTIFIC
EQUIPMENT.

688
00:44:25,830 --> 00:44:29,041
THIS OBELISK IS ONE HUGE
DEFLECTOR MECHANISM.

689
00:44:29,167 --> 00:44:31,628
IT IS IMPERATIVE
THAT WE GET INSIDE
IMMEDIATELY.

690
00:44:33,463 --> 00:44:36,799
CAPTAIN, WE DO NOT HAVE
MUCH TIME.

691
00:44:41,095 --> 00:44:42,180
McCOY.

692
00:44:49,521 --> 00:44:51,314
I DON'T KNOW HOW
TO GET INSIDE.

693
00:44:51,439 --> 00:44:53,191
IF WE ARE NOT ABLE
TO GAIN ENTRY

694
00:44:53,316 --> 00:44:54,900
AND ACTIVATE
THE DEFLECTOR
MECHANISM

695
00:44:55,026 --> 00:44:56,569
WITHIN THE NEXT
50 MINUTES,

696
00:44:56,693 --> 00:45:00,365
THIS ENTIRE PLANET
WILL BE DESTROYED.

697
00:45:00,490 --> 00:45:02,617
THE KEY MUST BE
IN THESE SYMBOLS.

698
00:45:02,741 --> 00:45:03,535
WE'VE GOT TO DECIPHER THEM.

699
00:45:03,660 --> 00:45:05,620
