A SERIES OF TONAL
QUALITIES

705
00:45:15,380 --> 00:45:16,922
SPOKEN IN THEIR
PROPER SEQUENCE.

706
00:45:17,048 --> 00:45:19,008
GIVE ME YOUR COMMUNICATOR.

707
00:45:19,133 --> 00:45:21,886
TONAL CONTROL,
CONSONANTS AND VOWELS--

708
00:45:22,011 --> 00:45:23,471
I MUST HAVE
HIT IT ACCIDENTALLY

709
00:45:23,596 --> 00:45:24,847
WHEN I CONTACTED
THE SHIP.

710
00:45:24,972 --> 00:45:27,642
IF YOU COULD
REMEMBER YOUR EXACT
WORDS, CAPTAIN.

711
00:45:32,021 --> 00:45:33,523
KIRK TO<i> ENTERPRISE.</i>

712
00:45:33,648 --> 00:45:35,774
Scott:
AYE, CAPTAIN.

713
00:45:38,444 --> 00:45:40,946
SCOTTY, IF THE DEFLECTOR
ISN'T ACTIVATED
WITHIN 20 MINUTES,

714
00:45:41,072 --> 00:45:42,365
GET OUT OF ORBIT.

715
00:45:42,490 --> 00:45:45,535
GET THE<i> ENTERPRISE</i>
OUT OF THE DANGER ZONE.

716
00:45:45,660 --> 00:45:47,370
THE LANDING PARTY
IS EXPENDABLE.

717
00:45:47,495 --> 00:45:49,247
THE<i> ENTERPRISE</i> ISN'T.

718
00:45:50,289 --> 00:45:52,291
KIRK OUT.

719
00:45:52,417 --> 00:45:54,001
MIRAMANEE.

720
00:45:56,295 --> 00:45:59,257
BONES, STAY WITH HER.

721
00:45:59,382 --> 00:46:00,883
DO WHAT YOU CAN.

722
00:46:11,561 --> 00:46:14,313
IT IS SIMILAR
TO DEFLECTOR PANELS
I'VE SEEN, CAPTAIN,

723
00:46:14,439 --> 00:46:16,982
BUT FAR MORE
COMPLICATED.

724
00:46:17,108 --> 00:46:18,526
CAREFUL.

725
00:46:18,651 --> 00:46:21,654
I MUST HAVE HIT
SOMETHING ACCIDENTALLY.

726
00:46:21,778 --> 00:46:23,780
THE BEAM CAUGHT ME,

727
00:46:23,906 --> 00:46:25,908
AND THAT'S WHEN
I STOPPED REMEMBERING.

728
00:46:26,033 --> 00:46:27,535
PROBABLY
A MEMORY BEAM.

729
00:46:27,660 --> 00:46:29,287
YOU MUST HAVE
ACTIVATED IT

730
00:46:29,412 --> 00:46:30,871
OUT OF SEQUENCE.

731
00:46:30,996 --> 00:46:33,082
THERE'S MORE SYMBOLS.

732
00:46:33,207 --> 00:46:34,250
CAN YOU READ THEM?

733
00:46:34,375 --> 00:46:35,543
I DO HAVE
AN EXCELLENT EYE

734
00:46:35,668 --> 00:46:36,919
FOR MUSICAL NOTES,
CAPTAIN.

735
00:46:37,044 --> 00:46:38,546
THEY WOULD SEEM
TO INDICATE

736
00:46:38,671 --> 00:46:39,922
THAT THIS SERIES
OF RELAYS

737
00:46:40,047 --> 00:46:41,257
ACTIVATED
IN THEIR PROPER--

738
00:46:41,382 --> 00:46:44,176
SPOCK, JUST PRESS
THE RIGHT BUTTON.

739
00:46:47,012 --> 00:46:49,348
[RUMBLING]

740
00:47:15,124 --> 00:47:17,543
HOW IS SHE?

741
00:47:17,669 --> 00:47:19,962
SHE HAD BAD
INTERNAL INJURIES, JIM.

742
00:47:20,087 --> 00:47:22,381
WILL SHE LIVE?

743
00:47:23,840 --> 00:47:24,592
NO.

744
00:47:52,370 --> 00:47:54,664
KIROK, IT IS TRUE.

745
00:47:54,789 --> 00:47:56,457
YOU ARE SAFE.

746
00:47:56,582 --> 00:47:59,627
AND SO ARE YOUR PEOPLE,
MIRAMANEE.

747
00:48:02,755 --> 00:48:06,801
I KNEW YOU WOULD
SAVE THEM, MY CHIEF.

748
00:48:10,095 --> 00:48:12,223
WHEN I AM BETTER...

749
00:48:12,348 --> 00:48:16,018
IT WILL BE
AS IT WAS,

750
00:48:16,143 --> 00:48:19,146
WILL IT...NOT?

751
00:48:19,980 --> 00:48:22,483
IF THAT'S WHAT YOU WANT.

752
00:48:25,069 --> 00:48:26,903
WE WILL LIVE

753
00:48:27,029 --> 00:48:29,782
LONG
AND HAPPY LIVES.

754
00:48:31,158 --> 00:48:33,035
I WILL BEAR YOU

755
00:48:33,160 --> 00:48:35,663
MANY STRONG SONS.

756
00:48:35,788 --> 00:48:37,790
[GROANS]

757
00:48:40,668 --> 00:48:45,172
I LOVE YOU ALWAYS.

758
00:48:47,675 --> 00:48:51,345
AND I LOVE YOU,
MIRAMANEE...

759
00:48:51,470 --> 00:48:53,389
ALWAYS.

760
00:49:05,109 --> 00:49:07,944
EACH KISS...

761
00:49:08,070 --> 00:49:10,823
IS AS THE FIRST.
